        section
          h2 Manual Evaluation
          h4 Adequacy
          ul
            li Does the translation contain all the information in the source?
            li Rated from (1=no meaning) to (5=all meaning)
          h4 Fluency
          ul
            li Does the translation sound natural?
            li Does it contain grammatical errors?
            li Rated from (1=incomprehensible) to (5=perfect)
        section
