          p First method with high correspondence between a machine's output and that of a human
          p Standard evaluation for MT (still)
          p Product of precision and a <em>brevity penalty</em>
          ul
            li Precision: how many of the machine's words are in the reference?
            li Brevity penalty: how long is the machine's output compared to the reference?
